      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint, showroom condition and has been meticulously cared for by a single owner. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep shine and no imperfections, while the interior remains in like-new condition with no signs of wear. Mechanically, it is perfect, having been serviced exclusively at authorized dealerships with a complete maintenance history available. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it left the showroom floor.",
