    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained vehicle that exemplifies consistent performance and reliability. This unit has undergone a comprehensive multi-point inspection to ensure it meets our rigorous standards for roadworthiness and aesthetic appeal. Featuring a well-preserved interior and a robust powertrain, it offers an exceptional balance of luxury and utility for the discerning driver. Experience the assurance of quality engineering at a highly competitive market valuation.",
      "price": 34900.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 33
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Thanks so much for stopping by to check out my car! This ride has been such a joy to own and it's still in wonderful shape, just waiting for someone new to take it on an adventure. It's been well-loved and runs like a charm, making it a super reliable choice for your daily commutes or weekend getaways. I'm really looking to get this to a great new home quickly, so I've priced it to move! If you have any questions at all, please don't hesitate to reach out\u2014I'm super happy to chat and tell you all about it!",
      "price": 29900.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 33
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six engine. This high-revving power plant delivers exceptional throttle response via individual throttle bodies and is mated to a crisp Getrag 420G six-speed manual transmission. Mechanically, the vehicle is sorted with a reinforced rear subframe to maintain lateral rigidity and a bulletproofed dual-VANOS system for optimal cam timing across the power band. The chassis retains its balance with a factory limited-slip differential and refreshed bushings to ensure precise turn-in. While showing minor cosmetic patina consistent with its age, the drivetrain remains robust, benefiting from recent rod bearing service and a cooling system overhaul. This is a mechanically sound example of an analog icon, ready for the apex.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 33
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Well-maintained. Clean title. Runs well. Ready for immediate sale.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 33
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "Up for sale is a beautifully maintained vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between luxury and everyday reliability. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, though close inspection reveals a few minor surface scratches and small stone chips typical of careful road use. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean; the upholstery is plush and free of any odors or significant wear, and every feature\u2014from the heated seats to the intuitive infotainment system\u2014works exactly as intended. Mechanically, this car is in top form, having benefited from a consistent maintenance schedule and a recent full-service check including new tires and a fresh oil change. It drives tight and quiet, offering a smooth power delivery that inspires confidence. This is an honest, well-cared-for machine ready for its next chapter without the need for any immediate investment.",
      "price": 36800.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 33
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exceptionally well-maintained vehicle, offering a superior balance of performance and long-term value. This specimen has been curated for the driver who demands mechanical integrity and a refined aesthetic. Featuring a robust service history and a clean, preserved interior, it represents a premier opportunity within its class. Our rigorous inspection process ensures that this vehicle delivers a reliable and sophisticated driving experience for its next owner.",
      "price": 34800.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 33
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I'm looking to find a new home for my awesome car. It\u2019s been super reliable and is still in really solid shape\u2014honestly, it drives like a dream! It\u2019s perfect for someone looking for a dependable ride that still looks great on the road. I've taken great care of it, and it's ready for its next adventure. Come take it for a spin, you\u2019re gonna love it! \u2728",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 33
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Available is a driver-spec E46 M3 powered by the high-revving S54 B32 inline-six engine, featuring individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. This example is equipped with the desirable 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox and a variable M differential lock for precise torque distribution. Mechanical integrity is prioritized: the VANOS system has been serviced, and the rear subframe has been reinforced to ensure structural longevity. The chassis remains taut with a factory-spec suspension setup and refreshed bushings, providing the communicative steering and balanced lateral dynamics inherent to the platform. While the exterior displays minor road-derived patina consistent with a well-maintained enthusiast vehicle, the powertrain delivers seamless, linear acceleration.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
